{"tid":1609760,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日有份荃灣既全部入尼，我有d野想講講","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:23:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:15:51.000Z","uid":280214,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8474a27c433cd0cee2e9ff1190e6719b6b4d6a30","tid":1609760,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:23:26.000Z","msg":"我想講今日大家做得好好，知道大家攰，或者好傷心，我今日都沉澱左好耐。明既唔完美  可接受  但需要改善。我諗咁多位巴絲都唔想見到再手手足中槍受傷，咁就單刀直入。<br />\n<br />\n首先，唔該上前線就full gear先上，何謂full gear?(頭盔 豬嘴 眼罩）必須，最好有遮。（之後補充）你地班偽勇武知唔知會累死人架沒gear行咁前只會比中後排覺得前線好有張力，到班狗一放TG沒gear果d又走得快撚過人，我屌你前線得返咁撚少人邊個補位？不過今日見到一班真既勇武系地面rust上前然後班沒咩gear既就上天橋尼波土魔法大家配合得好好。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做得好好</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其次，遮既作用！我見前線好多人都有遮但唔開唔，大家要記住長遮系好撚勁既一件gear基本上除左打狗、落雨遮人，佢可以擋曬班狗全部野（TG 橡膠彈 海綿彈等除實彈）唔該系前線有遮可遮然後半痞盡量等班狗唔系水平線射中你個頭，再者遮對於我地尼講系系盾應該用左手攞，而右手系我地既慣用手咁當然系攞我地既魔法用品，棍又好，魔法又好總之<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武器</span></span>一定系<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">右手</span></span>，同我記撚住。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗，救人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後我今日真系好自責，好內疚自己點解咁沒用，返到屋企喊左好耐，個巴打個浮板我認到，明明系隔離，之一秒有講有笑互想照應，下秒同我講中撚左實彈？一尼好無助，二尼好撚sad。各位巴絲我唔想再見到有人流血受傷比人拉，更加唔想有手足因為比班黑警搞到冇左條命。我地要將示威融入生活，咩方法都好對準政權，清算黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba58927e9a7cad46f3306979bab5edeb69665534","tid":1609760,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ce898a6493e6618932effdcb4fab439902a336","tid":1609760,"uid":10070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba70cde9d1d782499766cd04f53a3431aa5bab90","tid":1609760,"uid":308456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:51:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"de2e1510f0babde5b406b17b1e2533051e0a409d","tid":1609760,"uid":307195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:11.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"925824a50268baee6cd4f96760f28b1d1acdd039","tid":1609760,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再諗住喇巴打<br />\n休息下<br />\n<br />\n放鬆自己先"},{"pid":"2562e6d6b897afb550235600a425776cf0410a3c","tid":1609760,"uid":280214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"925824a50268baee6cd4f96760f28b1d1acdd039","tid":1609760,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:00:18.000Z","msg":"唔好再諗住喇巴打<br />\n休息下<br />\n<br />\n放鬆自己先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"休息返一排重整返心態先，我覺得依家同之前己經完全唔撚同<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20c18a137d26e6861d2dbe2a80c505c6ff9215a","tid":1609760,"uid":140710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:27:42.000Z","msg":"荃灣人要加油<br />\n今日真係好亂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e58078631cfc1d1c7960fccfaf7dd0dd5ccf2b","tid":1609760,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c7e5be00a936923175e0b075a79e990881a4a9ff","tid":1609760,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:06:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"df00b8e60e1ca0d7c3d1a4bcfe58456e04297da0","tid":1609760,"uid":280214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019